  Removing Andrej Kacian (Ticho) from metadata.xml (as per #59986).

  05 Apr 2008; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org>
  -policyd-weight-0.1.14.5.ebuild, -policyd-weight-0.1.14.14.ebuild,
  -policyd-weight-0.1.14.15.ebuild, policyd-weight-0.1.14.17.ebuild:
  Use virtual/perl-Sys-Syslog in DEPEND. Bug #211631, by Jakub Moc. Old
  ebuild cleanup.

  29 Mar 2008; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org>
  policyd-weight-0.1.14.17.ebuild:
  stable x86, security bug 214403

  29 Mar 2008; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org>
  policyd-weight-0.1.14.17.ebuild:
  Change default LOCKPATH value to /var/run/policyd-weight in config, it is
  safer there than in /tmp.

