*policyd-weight-0.1.14.15 (27 Mar 2008)

  27 Mar 2008; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org>
  -policyd-weight-0.1.14.3.ebuild, -policyd-weight-0.1.14.4.ebuild,
  +policyd-weight-0.1.14.15.ebuild:
